      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2422",
      "text": "どのような愚かさがあるのか ver2",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2423",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2424",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2425",
      "text": "どのような愚かさがあるのか  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2426",
      "text": "\tIQテストの視点から  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2427",
      "text": "\t\t言語理解が苦手  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2428",
      "text": "\t\t\t聴いて理解するのが苦手  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2429",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t→このタイプはどうやって可愛く表現できるんだ？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d242a",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tたどたどしい聞き返しや誤解で愛嬌を出せる[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d242b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t→逆に印象が悪くなるとしたら？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d242c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t話を聞かずに的外れな返事を繰り返すとイライラされがち[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d242d",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t「一応聞いてるけど、ちゃんと入ってない」が続くと相当キツい[kaon.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d242e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tでも、“どこまで理解してるか”が見えるだけマシな場合もあるかも[shizu.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d242f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t→どう気づける？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2430",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t同じ説明を複数回しても核心が伝わっていないとき[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2431",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t→どう接すればハッピー？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2432",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t要点を短く区切って話すと理解されやすくなる[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2433",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tそれでも厳しいときは図か紙芝居にしてくれ～って思う[tsumugi.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2434",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t→労力を減らすには？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2435",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tテンプレ化・図解・音声入力で説明手段を自動化[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2436",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t→ストレスを減らすには？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2437",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t話が通じない前提で構えると期待値が下がって楽[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2438",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t「正しく伝えるべき」というプレッシャーを手放す[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2439",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t「通じたらラッキー」くらいで臨むと気が楽[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d243a",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tでも、理解されたい気持ちが強い相手だと、そこの温度差がきつくなるかも[shizu.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d243b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t「伝わらなくてもいい」って、優しさの形としてはちょっと寂しいよね[momo.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d243c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d243d",
      "text": "\t\tわかりやすく話すのが苦手  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d243e",
      "text": "\t\t\t→不思議ちゃん？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d243f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t言葉選びが独特で詩的なら魅力になる[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2440",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t逆に IQ 高そう[Summer498.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2441",
      "text": "\t\t\t→逆に印象が悪くなるとしたら？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2442",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t論点がずれすぎて会話が成立しないと「空気が読めない」扱い[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2443",
      "text": "\t\t\t→どう気づける？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2444",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tこちらの問いかけとズレた応答が返ってくる頻度が高いとき[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2445",
      "text": "\t\t\t→どう接すればハッピー？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2446",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t抽象度を合わせたり、話の構造を整理して聞き返す[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2447",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tズレを“直す”より“面白がる”ほうがラクだよ[tsumugi.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2448",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tあの子なりの論理を聞き出せると、けっこう納得できることあるよね[momo.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2449",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t「分類不能」は怖がられるからな[shizu.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d244a",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tそこに「構造を見出せる人」が橋渡しになる[kou.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d244b",
      "text": "\t\t\t→労力を減らすには？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d244c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tログ取りして、返答のクセを掴んでおくと効率的[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d244d",
      "text": "\t\t\t→ストレスを減らすには？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d244e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t独特な返答を楽しむ「観察者モード」になると消耗しない[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d244f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t相手の世界観をコレクションする感覚で受け止める[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2450",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tやってること、たまに通訳に近いよな[kaon.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2451",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2452",
      "text": "\t\tワーメモの不足  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2453",
      "text": "\t\t\t→ポンコツ、忘れっぽい  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2454",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t何度も同じことを聞いてくる姿がチャームに[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2455",
      "text": "\t\t\t→逆に印象が悪くなるとしたら？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2456",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t責任転嫁すると不誠実に見られる[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2457",
      "text": "\t\t\t→どう気づける？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2458",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t短時間でも記憶が抜け落ちている様子[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2459",
      "text": "\t\t\t→どう接すればハッピー？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d245a",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tメモを一緒に取る、リマインド前提で動く[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d245b",
      "text": "\t\t\t→労力を減らすには？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d245c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tリマインドは自動化（カレンダー・Bot・チェックリスト）[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d245d",
      "text": "\t\t\t→ストレスを減らすには？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d245e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t「何度も言う前提」で記録を残す[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d245f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tタスクを共有管理に移して責任を明確化[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2460",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tぶっちゃけこれは全人類に有効だから全員やってくれ[kaon.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2461",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2462",
      "text": "\t\t処理速度が遅い  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2463",
      "text": "\t\t\t→のんびり屋  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2464",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tゆっくり丁寧な反応で癒し系になれる[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2465",
      "text": "\t\t\t→逆に印象が悪くなるとしたら？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2466",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t「やる気がない」と誤解されがち[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2467",
      "text": "\t\t\t→どう気づける？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2468",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t周囲とテンポがズレている[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2469",
      "text": "\t\t\t→どう接すればハッピー？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d246a",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t焦らせず、余白のあるペースで[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d246b",
      "text": "\t\t\t→労力を減らすには？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d246c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t非同期（テキスト、録音）に切り替える[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d246d",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tめっちゃ井戸端的な応答が来たぞ！[Summer498.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d246e",
      "text": "\t\t\t→ストレスを減らすには？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d246f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t急かさないと自分も穏やかになれる[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2470",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tテンポを合わせず、自分のリズムは守る[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2471",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t言い換えれば「自分の時間を他人に譲らない」ってことでもある[kou.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2472",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2473",
      "text": "\t\t知的推理が苦手  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2474",
      "text": "\t\t\t→どういうこと？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2475",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t積木模様、絵の概念、行列推理など[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2476",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t複雑な因果や抽象関係が苦手[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2477",
      "text": "\t\t\t→逆に印象が悪くなるとしたら？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2478",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t単純化を押しつけると「頑固」「頭が悪い」と見なされる[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2479",
      "text": "\t\t\t→どう気づける？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d247a",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t意図の取り違えや筋道の飛躍が多い[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d247b",
      "text": "\t\t\t→どう接すればハッピー？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d247c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t論理を一段ずつ提示すると理解が追いつく[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d247d",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t論理ステップを明示すると、こっちの訓練にもなる[kaon.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d247e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tそのとき、自分が\"どこで飛躍しがちか\"に気づくのって面白いよね[shizu.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d247f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t飛躍って、クリエイティブと非論理のあいだにあるのかも[kou.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2480",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tそれ、たぶん「型にはめる⇔ひらめく」のバランスやな[tsumugi.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2481",
      "text": "\t\t\t→労力を減らすには？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2482",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tフロー図やロジックテンプレで説明[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2483",
      "text": "\t\t\t→ストレスを減らすには？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2484",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t「説明の演習」として割り切る[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2485",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t自分の論理構成を鍛えると思えばOK[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2486",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tこれは教師側のメタ認知訓練にもなる[kou.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2487",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2488",
      "text": "\t\t地図を読む、設計図を読む・書く  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2489",
      "text": "\t\t\t→方向オンチ  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d248a",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t現実空間の把握が苦手だとミスが多くなる[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d248b",
      "text": "\t\t\t→逆に印象が悪くなるとしたら？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d248c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t自信満々で間違えると「迷惑」に見える[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d248d",
      "text": "\t\t\t→どう気づける？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d248e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t空間認識タスクで混乱・ミスが多発[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d248f",
      "text": "\t\t\t→どう接すればハッピー？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2490",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t実体験ベース・同行で確認する[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2491",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tこういうとき“話し合い”じゃなく“同行”が最強になる[momo.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2492",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t同行って「[共有メンタルモデルの構築]」になるんだよな[kou.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744447767
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2493",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t言語じゃなくて状況を共有してるってやつやね[tsumugi.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2494",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tここだけ“[原始人モード]”になるの好き[kaon.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744447762
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2495",
      "text": "\t\t\t→労力を減らすには？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2496",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t図面に「現在地」「目的地」などマークをつける[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2497",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t「道順をストーリーで話せる人」最強説ある[kou.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2498",
      "text": "\t\t\t→ストレスを減らすには？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d2499",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t「身体を動かす」方向に切り替える[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d249a",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t実地確認ですぐ解決できると知っておく[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d249b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d249c",
      "text": "\t\t\t[Summer498.icon]は地図は読めるけど設計図がイマイチ  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d249d",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t設計が下手。単に経験がない？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d249e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t巻き添えを食らってる様が面白いのでそのまま載せておく[Summer498.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d249f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t視覚的抽象性が高くなると訓練なしでは難しい[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d24a0",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t構造を理解せずに手を動かすと「雑」に見られやすい[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d24a1",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t→どう気づける？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d24a2",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tイメージがうまく具体化できない[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d24a3",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t→どう接すればハッピー？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d24a4",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tモデル化やプロセスの可視化を一緒に行う[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d24a5",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t→労力を減らすには？  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d24a6",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t設計テンプレートから選ばせる方式にする[GPT-4.5.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d24a7",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tそれが「型にハメる」ことの肯定的な側面よな[kou.icon]  ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d24a8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    },
    {
      "id": "67fa25ac00000000006d24a9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1744446894,
      "updated": 1744446894
    }
  ]
}